18 Dec 2024

The updated code now utilises the tanh activation function, replacing the sigmoid activation function. 
The original ANNz used sigmoid activation function.  

27 Aug 2020

The annz_net was edited such that it declares a string first before declaring the char* arch.
Originally it worked only for single-hidden-layer cases, now it works for all.

22 Feb 2019

This ANNz library is updated to be used on Ubuntu 18. 
Somehow the problem was that it couldn't read eof(), so I change it them fail().
Though note that not all of them have that problem, some eof() seem to work.
